metadata.description:
Top OPM Hits Philippines 2025 🎶 July Trending Mix | Best Tagalog Songs on Spotify & YouTube

🎧 Welcome to Midnight Tears – your cozy spot for the most emotional and trending OPM Tagalog love songs of 2025! 🇵🇭💘

This July mix features the Top OPM Hits in the Philippines, trending on Spotify, YouTube, and TikTok — with heartfelt lyrics, nostalgic vibes, and music that speaks to your soul 🥀

✨ Kicking off this playlist are 5 standout tracks that define the sound of Filipino love and heartbreak in 2025:

💔 PWEDE BANG? – Hev Abi: A raw and catchy hip-hop track about hesitation and hidden feelings, making waves with Gen Z listeners 🎤
🌫️ Multo – Cup Of Joe: Haunting and poetic, this viral ballad captures the feeling of being haunted by memories 🌙
👀 Tingin – Cup Of Joe: Romantic and relatable, it hits like a sweet confession of love at first glance 💌
🖤 Naiilang – Le John: A quiet emotional storm, this mellow track is all about unspoken love and awkward silence 🫢
🌌 Saksi Ang Langit – December Avenue: A classic in the making, with lyrics that ache and melodies that stick with you long after 💭

These songs, and many more in this mix, are perfect for:
💬 Late-night reflections
🚘 Rainy road trips
💔 Healing a broken heart
🌠 Or simply vibing with Tagalog love songs that understand you.
